{"tid":2489876,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網售「我不是中國人」衫 官媒轟歧視","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T08:46:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"87f435c83ca87292b53824649e245ce2e2ca6d0b","tid":2489876,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210414/FIW4HGKCJRGKTHODDP4DLNMNNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210414%2FFIW4HGKCJRGKTHODDP4DLNMNNA%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sOrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=3cacf70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210414%2FFIW4HGKCJRGKTHODDP4DLNMNNA%2F&h=28d0b172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210414/FIW4HGKCJRGKTHODDP4DLNMNNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n網售「我不是中國人」衫 官媒轟歧視<br />\n<br />\n近來在美國針對亞裔的仇恨情緒高漲，多地發生辱罵甚至襲擊事件，不少亞裔認為是受中國人牽連。有海外網上購物平台上載寫明「I&rsquo;m not Chinese」（我不是中國人）的產品，昨被中國官媒《環球時報》怒轟「醜陋」，痛斥「歧視中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《環時》痛斥醜陋<br />\n<br />\n《環時》點名批評外國網上購物平台Redbubble，稱只要在平台搜索欄輸入「I&rsquo;m not Chinese」，就會有T恤、手機殼、口罩及杯等相關字句產品，不少列明自己是亞洲人，但屬於其他國家，如泰國人、日本人等。報道指部份更寫「Don&rsquo;t Shoot I&rsquo;m not Chinese（不要開槍，我不是中國人）」。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》痛斥這些作品「醜陋」及「歧視中國人」，「那些仇恨亞裔的人，可不會在行兇前判斷受害者是哪國人。在上個月震驚全美的亞特蘭大連環槍擊案中，受害的六名亞裔裏就有四名韓裔女性」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者在Redbubble查閱，已找不到「Don&rsquo;t Shoot I&rsquo;m not Chinese」T恤（圖），惟見到零星「I&rsquo;m not Chinese」產品，亦可找到撐中國人產品，如「I&rsquo;m Not Yelling I&rsquo;m A Proud Chinese」（我不大吼 我是一個驕傲的中國人）。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4pelHTgArnPdqfH9bkryANEbwV4=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3SZYBBODZBCNHGFHJFPDBH7SLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4pelHTgArnPdqfH9bkryANEbwV4%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3SZYBBODZBCNHGFHJFPDBH7SLM.jpg&h=e9e20abc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"639f5aa520853cb8d557209356d47073e5f0e6cd","tid":2489876,"uid":371001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"一早就要咁做"},{"pid":"e3a46362eb87304cdc2ba8040bde4903817f65b2","tid":2489876,"uid":289978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"4月15全球#我不是中國人 日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma74WsLJxEdeR4r6VD8VYdW3U6iTbzoxWcjvnnWZEWVBv?filename=wyX7FCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyX7FCJ.png&h=6d203742&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYknKQem5c8GH64GvMVfmAJknCLWBrFeBWESDiuDCD41P?filename=eLBz44p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLBz44p.png&h=792a74c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad884dbb8fe02de5922fdf7b8289cf97aa5242c0","tid":2489876,"uid":199893,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"人地係韓國人話自己唔係中國人係講緊事實<br />\n關支那撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地仲可以唔係日本人 唔係香港人 唔係泰國人添<br />\n又唔見其他國家會玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講事實就歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaf0f815f6a25cddd428873f38b551996700b4a","tid":2489876,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad884dbb8fe02de5922fdf7b8289cf97aa5242c0","tid":2489876,"uid":199893,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"人地係韓國人話自己唔係中國人係講緊事實<br />\n關支那撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地仲可以唔係日